Hi Kurt,

I finally received feedback from the engineering team.
Turning Reporting V2 on from System Configuration -> System setting should fix the missing destination details:


Please note that for older logs, the destination will not be available anymore. You will see just the new ones, after you enable the feature. 

Best regards,
Botond Biro | Technical Support Engineer
